name: Calamari
description: Calamari is a recipe prepared with squid, usually (but not always) battered and deep-fried.

name: Ceasar Salad
description: A Caesar salad is a green salad of romaine lettuce and croutons dressed with lemon juice, olive oil, egg, Worcestershire sauce, anchovies, garlic, Dijon mustard, Parmesan cheese, and black pepper. In its original form, this salad was prepared and served tableside.

name: Nachos
description: Nachos is a dish from northern Mexico that consists of tortilla chips (or totopos) covered with mince and cheese or a cheese-based sauce often served as a snack.
